title: Skiller vs Alem - Final - 3rd Beatbox Battle World Championship
description: Watch the final round between Skiller from Bulgaria vs Alem from France. They both were battling face to face on the main stage of the 3rd Beatbox Battle World Championship in Germany. The event took place at the Astra Kulturhaus Berlin in 2012 - Audio mastering by DaSka Records.
